==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: Know the astronomy above, and know the geography below.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: shàng zhī tīan wén, xìa zhī dì lĭ

===Phrase===
'''[[上]][[知]][[天文]]，[[下]][[知]][[地理]]'''

# (''idiom'') Describes someone who is very learned; a [[polymath]].

